headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Regional Banks Slump on Worries About Bad Loans; Data Storage Stocks Surge
summary: Regional bank stocks lost ground after a pair of banks disclosed issues with bad and fraudulent loans, while data storage stocks gained in the wake of price-target hikes from analysts.
